Module: autocycle
Author: Brian Weiss <brian@epicsol.org>

Description:
   Automatically cycles empty and op-less channels.

Config Variables:
   AUTO_CYCLE                - Boolean. Turns auto-cycle on/off.

Notes:
   This feature is far from fool-proof. It has been known to cause trouble,
   especially when connected to multiple servers in a single EPIC session.
   Use at your own risk.

